source: Proceed into the forest.{#Name="説明文"}

source: Argh! Zero's made it all the way here!?{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: No! NOOOO! ...Wait, which one is Zero?{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: No! NOOOO! ...Wait, which one is Zero?{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: The creepy chick with the hair, man! What the hell?{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: The creepy chick with the hair, man! What the hell?{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Men! Our foe is an Intoner! Break formation and give her all you've got!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Men! Our foe is an Intoner! Break formation and give her all you've got!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Understood, sir! Get her!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Understood, sir! Get her!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Where's Lady Three?{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Where's Lady Three?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Safe with Octa, I hope!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Safe with Octa, I hope!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Then we must protect the both of them!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Then we must protect the both of them!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: This is hopeless! We can't even scratch 'em!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: This is hopeless! We can't even scratch 'em!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Pull your head out of your ass and keep fighting!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Pull your head out of your ass and keep fighting!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: So now we have to search the whole damn{LF}forest on foot for this stupid shrine?{#Name="Dito"}
source: So now we have to search the whole damn{LF}forest on foot for this stupid shrine?{#Name="Dito"}

source: Cram it. And be thankful you've still got a foot to search on.{#Name="Zero"}

source: まだかな？　まだかな？{#Name="ミハイル"}

source: What are you going on about, dummy?{#Name="Zero"}

source: Trees with faces.{#Name="Zero"}

source: Yeah! I said hi to one because I thought{LF}he was smiling at me! Funny, huh?{#Name="Mikhail"}

source: The only thing funny is how dumb you are.{#Name="Zero"}
